  button(class='collapsible') Brainstorming ▼
  div(class='technique-table')
    table
      tr
        th Definition
        th Example
      tr
        td A method of problem solving that involves getting together a group of five to ten persons to consider a problem. The participants are to suggest whatever idea pops into their heads, no matter how weird, in the hope that a creative solution will be found (Dictionary of Statistics & Methodology)
        td #[a(href="https://sites.tufts.edu/digitalhumanities/brainstorming-your-project/") Brainstorming Your Project – DH at Tufts]
  br
  button(class='collapsible') Browsing ▼
